snippet.title: Defenders of Avarax – a Space Marine 2 VR Experience
snippet.description:
Head to Zero Latency with your mates, because there's a brand new VR experience where up to eight players can team up to take down Tyranids, based on the Space Marine 2. Get into the game in a whole new way. https://ow.ly/7nfR50TnSz6
